text: Didier Migaud (born 6 June 1952) is a French politician. He was the Minister of Justice from 21 September 2024 to 23 December 2024. He was president of the French Cour des comptes from 2010 to 2020, and member of the National Assembly of France from 1988 to 2010. ==References== Category:1952 births Category:Living people Category:French politicians Category:People from Tours
title: Didier Migaud
